# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ClaimLens environment configuration
#
# SETUP:
#   1. Copy this file to `.env.local`  (cp .env.local.example .env.local)
#   2. Paste your key after the `=` below.
#   3. Restart the dev server.
#
# Get a free key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#
# `.env.local` is gitignored, so your key can never be committed by accident.
#
# NOTE: The app runs fine WITHOUT a key. With no key set, the three bundled
# sample claims resolve from cached responses and the UI shows a "Demo Mode"
# badge. Only live photo uploads require a key.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional. Defaults to gemini-2.5-flash (stable, multimodal, free tier).
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
